window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The rains have halted, and all that’s left is mud.</b></p> <p>Mud...and the tracks of the Goblin Lord’s army. They have finally come to Liscor, pursued by Tyrion Veltras and his forces. In their path lies The Wandering Inn. Erin Solstice will have to find a way to survive the coming conflict, and save her friends. The question is: at what cost?</p>"; 
